de.timmyrs.suprdiscordbot

Class Main

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.timmyrs.suprdiscordbot.Main

  • public class Main
extends java.lang.Object
    SuprDiscordBot Main Class.

    Arguments:

    • --debug makes output more verbose and makes DiscordAPI.isInDebugMode() return true
    • --dont-update-scripts stops the Script Watcher from checking for new or updated scripts. This is recommended for a production environment, as the watcher reads on your hard drive quite often.
    Author:
    timmyRS
    See Also:
    DiscordAPI, ScriptAPI, ConsoleAPI, Guild
